[section#mdspan.sub.map.common
    [:en] Common
    [:zh_CN] 一般信息
]

[para]
[:en] The following elements apply to all functions in [#mdspan.sub.map].
[:zh_CN] 以下各项适用于 [#mdspan.sub.map] 中的所有函数。

[para:constraints]
[:en] [`sizeof...(SliceSpecifiers)] equals [`extents_type::rank()],
[`SliceSpecifiers...`[[$k]`]] is a valid [`submdspan] slice type
for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`Extents].
[:zh_CN] [`sizeof...(SliceSpecifiers)] 等于 [`extents_type::rank()]，
[`SliceSpecifiers...`[[$k]`]] 是 [`Extents] 的第 [$k] 个尺度的有效 [`submdspan] 分片类型。

[para:expects]
[:en] For each rank index [$k] of [`extents()],
[`slices...`[[$k]`]] is a valid slice for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`extents()].
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`extents()] 的每个秩索引，[`slices...`[[$k]`]] 是 [`extents()] 的
第 [$k] 个尺度的有效分片。

[para]
[:en] Let [`sub_ext] be the result of [`subextents(extents(), slices...)]
and let [`SubExtents] be [`decltype(sub_ext)].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`sub_ext] 为 [`subextents(extents(), slices...)] 的结果，
并令 [`SubExtents] 为 [`decltype(sub_ext)]。

[para]
[:en] Let [`sub_strides] be an [`array<SubExtents::index_type, SubExtents::rank()>]
such that for each rank index [$k] of [`extents()] for which the type of
[`slices...`[[$k]`]] is not a collapsing slice type, [`sub_strides`[[^MAP_RANK](slices,[$k])`]] equals:
[:zh_CN] 令 [`sub_strides] 为某个 [`array<SubExtents::index_type, SubExtents::rank()>]，
使得对于 [`extents()] 中每个使 [`slices...`[[$k]`]] 的类型不是折叠分片类型的秩索引 [$k]，
[`sub_strides`[[^MAP_RANK](slices,[$k])`]]：

[list]
[item]
[:en] [`stride(k) * s.stride] if the type of [`s] is a specialization of [`extent_slice]
and [`s.extent > 1] is [`true], where [`s] is [`slices...`[[$k]`]];
[:zh_CN] 当 [`s] 的类型是 [`extent_slice] 的特例且 [`s.extent > 1] 为 [`true] 时，
等于 [`stride(k) * s.stride]，其中 [`s] 为 [`slices...`[[$k]`]]；

[item]
[:en] otherwise, [`stride([$k])].
[:zh_CN] 否则，等于 [`stride([$k])]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Let [`ls] be a pack of values of [`index_type], where the [$\rho^\text{th}]
element equals the lower bound of the [`submdspan] slice range of [`slices...`[[$\rho$]`]]
for extent [$\rho] of [`extents()].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`ls] 为 [`index_type] 的一组值，其中第 [$\rho] 个元素等于
[`extents()] 的尺度 [$\rho] 的 [`slices...`[[$\rho$]`]] 的 [`submdspan] 分片范围的下界。

[para]
[:en] If [`ls...`[[$k]`]] equals [`extents().extent([$k])] for any rank index [$k] of [`extents()],
then let [`offset] be a value of type [`size_t] equal to [`required_span_size()].
[:zh_CN] 如果对于 [`extents()] 的任何秩索引 [$k]，[`ls...`[[$k]`]] 都等于
[`extents().extent([$k])]，则令 [`offset] 为等于 [`required_span_size()] 的 [`size_t] 类型的值。

[:en] Otherwise, let [`offset] be a value of type [`size_t] equal to [`operator()(ls...)].
[:zh_CN] 否则，令 [`offset] 为等于 [`operator()(ls...)] 的 [`size_t] 类型的值。
